f line-driven\ndisk winds in AGN/QSO, it will be critical to include a more detailed treatment\nof radiative transfer and ionization in the next generation of hydrodynamic\nsimulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Feb 2014 12:31:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Feb 2014 13:48:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 May 2014 08:57:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
